There are several [[impact crater]]s named '''Herschel''' in the [[Solar System]], although the best known is the huge crater on [[Saturn]]'s moon [[Mimas (moon)|Mimas]]. Most are named after the eighteenth-century astronomer [[William Herschel]].
*[[Herschel (lunar crater)]], on the Moon *[[Herschel (Martian crater)]], on Mars *[[Herschel (Mimantean crater)]], on Mimas *[[J. Herschel (crater)]] - a lunar crater named after John Herschel *[[C. Herschel (crater)]] - a lunar crater named after Caroline Herschel
